ActDivorce Act
Family Orders and Agreements Enforcement Assistance Act
Garnishment, Attachment and Pension Diversion Act
SubjectOrder Fixing November 15, 2023 as the Day on Which Certain Provisions of An Act to amend the Divorce Act, the Family Orders and Agreements Enforcement Assistance Act and the Garnishment, Attachment and Pension Diversion Act and to make consequential amendments to another Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing November 15, 2023 as the day on which sections 43, 45, 46 and 48 and subsections 49(1), (3) and (5) to (7) of AN ACT TO AMEND THE DIVORCE ACT, THE FAMILY ORDERS AND AGREEMENTS ENFORCEMENT ASSISTANCE ACT AND THE GARNISHMENT, ATTACHMENT AND PENSION DIVERSION ACT AND TO MAKE CONSEQUENTIAL AMENDMENTS TO ANOTHER ACT, chapter 16 of the Statutes of Canada, 2019, COMES INTO FORCE in order to bring into force the amendments to Part I of the Family Orders and Agreement Enforcement Assistance Act.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2023-0019 Publication Date: 2023-06-21
AttachmentsAttachment
